headline: A Look At Accenture (ACN) Valuation After Recent Share Price Weakness
summary: Recent share performance and what it might signal Accenture (ACN) has been under pressure recently, with the stock showing a 12% decline over the past month and a smaller 2% decline over the past 3 months. Over a longer horizon, the year to date total return sits at a 7% decline, while the past year shows a 36% decline and the past 3 years an 11% decline, with a modest 1% gain over 5 years. These figures give you a snapshot of how the market has recently priced Accenture relative to its own...
